data.description: Priced to sell - Motivated Seller! LOCATION!! ** BELLAIRE BEACH on the doorstep. Next to HCA Largo (Hospital). How ideal is that! With no HOA this could be an ideal forever home, or rental income! Biltmore Estates is close to Downtown Largo with all the shopping, cafe's and restaurants. Taylor Park is nearby with the lots of wildlife to see and a lovely lake walk. What is there not to love about this 2 bed 2 bath home (Florida room was converted and is currently being used as a 3rd bedroom) that has a desirable fitted kitchen with modern appliances, upgraded master bathroom, spacious living, dining area and family room in a very desirable situation. Come see for yourself! ** SELLER IS VERY MOTIVATED  ** Not in a flood zone!! ** ALL INFORMATION IS DEEMED ACCURATE - BUYER AND BUYERS AGENT TO VERIFY  **
